divs: Sighting DetailsTHIS JUST HAPPEND...Just went outside to have a smoke. Bored, i flashed a lazer pointer up to sky, 4 quick flashes. Got a huge bright flash back. Excited as hell i started flashing more, KEPT GETTING FLASHES BACK! ended up with a total of 3 bright white almost blueish flashes back and 1 small red one, same spot, and WAY up right off oriens shoulder. the flashes where about the same size as my fingernail if held up to the sky i suppose. So incredible, i mean they were super bright and perfectly square. had the chills for about 15 minutes after and feel refrehes and energized for lack of better words. sorry for the typos im just so excited lol
